Package net.antidot.api.search

Interface Summary
ConnectorInterface Antidot search engine connector interface.
FacetValueHelperInterface Interface representing one facet value.
FeedCoderInterface Interface for coder of feed values.
FilterCoderInterface Interface for coder of filters and filter values.
TextFormatter Interface to format output text at your convenience.
 

Class Summary
BasicTextFormatter Basic string formatter.
CoderBase Base class for coder.
CoderManager Entry point for feed and filter coders.
Connector Antidot search engine connector.
DefaultFeedCoder Default implementation for feed coder.
DefaultFilterCoder Default implementation for filter coder.
Facet Facet configuration.
FacetHelper Helper to access main facet data from Antidot search engine reply.
FacetRegistry Register for all configured facets.
FacetValueBuilder Simplify the build of facet values.
IntervalFacetValueHelper Represents one value of interval facet.
MetaHelper Helper to access main meta data from Antidot search engine reply.
PagerHelper Helper to access pager information for a given reply set.
ProtobufExtensionManager Simple manager which registers necessary Google extensions.
Query Immutable query object.
QueryCoder Encodes/decodes queries.
QueryManager Manages query.
RepliesHelper Main helper to manager Antidot search engine replies.
ReplyHelper Helper for one reply.
ReplySetHelper Helper to access replies from one feed.
TreeFacetValueHelper Represent one value of a facet.
 

Enum Summary
FacetCombination Combination of the values of the facet.
FacetMode Management of new facet value.
FacetStickyness Sticky characteristic of facets.
FacetType Type of the facet.
 

Exception Summary
IncompleteReplySetException Invalid reply is provided by Antidot search engine.
ReplyException Base class for internal runtime exception.
